Ruby on Rails app :: Lilypond in a webapp.

Lilydocs is available for anyone to use at http://lilydocs.com ! If you want tinker the "source" with it go ahead and clone this repository.

note: lilydocs is configured to always use https in the 'production' evironment.

There are settings to be configured if you want to run this app.

They are in config/environment.rb.template and config/environment/production.rb.template. look for the "raise" statements.

